The IOT device chosen to collect the data is a a RaspberryPi. The IMU is connected to the RPi. It collects muliple readings and provides this data to the Rpi. The Rpi creates a dataset with 4 datapoints and publishes this to the broker under the topic doorData. 

Execution: 

	>Navigate to the folder which contains the code client.py
	>Exceute client.py
